item.description:
Come join us prepare and package food for those in need in the Greater Boston
area.


From the organization: We ask that everyone be 100% healthy and wear
pants or long skirts, shoes that cover and protect feet and a shirt that has at
least a t-shirt length sleeve. We have parking on the property, first come first
serve. We are on the Orange Line, Stony Brook Stop


Contact Catherine at localservice@bostonrotaract to sign up or for more information.
